The,Royal,Mail,Tracking,API,allows,your,customers,to,check,on,the,tracking,status,of,their,parcels,and,mail,items,The,API,provides,the,latest,tracking,information,the,tracking,history,and,the,proof,of,delivery,information,minus,the,signature,image,for,a,single,mail,item,The,API,provides,the,same,functionality,as,the,Track,Trace,section,on,the,Royal,Mail,website,direct,to,your,customers,There,are,no,costs,to,customers,for,using,the,Tracking,API,services,however,development,costs,must,be,covered,by,the,customer,Royal,Mail,will,not,accept,any,responsibility,for,these,development,implementation,and,testing,costs